{"word":"G373 - ἀναπαύω - anapaúō - an-ap-ow'-o - Take ease","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναπαύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>anapaúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>an-ap-ow'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Take ease"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இளைப்பாறுதல் தா, இளைப்பாறு, ஆறுதலடை, தங்கியிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to give oneself rest, take rest, to refresh"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G3973 - παύω - paúō - pow'-o/3973\">G3973</a>; (reflexively) to <i>repose</i> (literally or figuratively (be <i>exempt</i>), <i>remain</i>); by implication to <i>refresh:</i> - take ease, refresh, (give, take) rest."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1879 - ἐπαναπαύομαι - epanapaúomai - ep-an-ah-pow'-om-ahee/1879\">G1879</a>, <a href=\"#/G372 - ἀνάπαυσις - anápausis - an-ap'-ow-sis/372\">G372</a>, <a href=\"#/G373 - ἀναπαύω - anapaúō - an-ap-ow'-o/373\">G373</a>"}]}